n><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the city,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلْيَنظُرْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and let him see</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَيُّهَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">which is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَزْكَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the purest</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">طَعَامًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">food,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلْيَأْتِكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and let him bring to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِرِزْقٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">provision</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from it,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلْيَتَلَطَّفْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and let him be cautious.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا يُشْعِرَنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And let not be aware</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">about you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَحَدًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">anyone."</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>19<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 18-20" id="20" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Indeed, [they]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَظْهَرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they come to know</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">about you,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَرْجُمُوكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they will stone you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُعِيدُوكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">return you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِلَّتِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their religion.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And never</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُفْلِحُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will you succeed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَبَدًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">ever."</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>20<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
