<p class="ayah 18-29" id="29" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقُلِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْحَقُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"The truth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَّبِّكُمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your Lord,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَمَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so whoever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَآءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">wills -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلْيُؤْمِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">let him believe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and whoever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَآءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">wills -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلْيَكْفُرْ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">let him disbelieve."</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, We</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَعْتَدْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">have prepared</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar qura