<p class="ayah 18-30" id="30" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَمِلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and did</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the good deeds,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">indeed, We</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا نُضِيعُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will not let go waste</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَجْرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) reward</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of one) who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَحْسَنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">does good</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَمَلاً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">deeds.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>30<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
