first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَهَبٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">gold</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَلْبَسُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and will wear</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ثِيَابًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">garments,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خُضْرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">green,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سُندُسٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">fine silk</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِسْتَبْرَقٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and heavy brocade,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّتَّكِــِٔينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">reclining</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">therein</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">on</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَرَآئِكِ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">adorned couches.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نِعْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Excellent</span></span><span class="word staticW