<p class="ayah 18-56" id="56" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نُرْسِلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We send</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُرْسَلِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Messengers</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُبَشِّرِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(as) bearers of glad tidings</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمُنذِرِينَ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and (as) warners.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيُجَـٰدِلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And dispute</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَفَرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">disbelieve</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْبَـٰطِلِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with falsehood,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِيُدْحِضُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to refute</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">thereby</span></span><span class="wo