<p class="ayah 18-57" id="57" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَظْلَمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) more wrong</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِمَّن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">than (he) who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذُكِّرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">is reminded</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِـَٔـايَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of the Verses</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) his Lord,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَأَعْرَضَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but turns away</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَنْهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from them,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَنَسِىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and forgets</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَدَّمَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">have sent forth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَدَاهُ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">his hands?</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, We</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَعَلْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[We] have placed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">over</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلُوبِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their hearts</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَكِنَّةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">coverings,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">lest</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَفْقَهُوهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they understand it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَفِىٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَاذَانِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their ears</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقْرًا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) deafness.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَدْعُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you call them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></s