d staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّوْعِدٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) an appointment,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">never</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَجِدُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they will find</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن دُونِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">other than it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَوْئِلاً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">an escape.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>58<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 18-59" id="59" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَتِلْكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And these</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقُرَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] towns,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَهْلَكْنَـٰهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We destroyed them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ظَلَمُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they wronged,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَجَعَلْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and We made</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِمَهْلِكِهِم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for their destruction</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّوْعِدًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">an appointed time.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>59<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
