<p class="ayah 18-61" id="61" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">But when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَلَغَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they reached</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَجْمَعَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the junction</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَيْنِهِمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">between them,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَسِيَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they forgot</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حُوتَهُمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their fish,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱتَّخَذَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and it took</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَبِيلَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">its way</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">into</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْبَحْرِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the sea,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَرَبًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">slipping away.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>61<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 18-62" id="62" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَاوَزَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they had passed beyond</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he said</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِفَتَـٰهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to his boy,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَاتِنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Bring us</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">غَدَآءَنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">our morning meal.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَقَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Certainly</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَقِينَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">we have suffered</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَفَرِنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">our journey</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَـٰذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">this,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَصَبًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">fatigue."</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>62<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
