<p class="ayah 18-76" id="76" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"If</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَأَلْتُكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">I ask you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">about</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَىْءِۭ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">anything</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَعْدَهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">after it,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then (do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُصَـٰحِبْنِى‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">keep me as a companion.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Verily,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَلَغْتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you have reached</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن لَّدُنِّى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from me</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عُذْرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">an excuse."</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket">