<p class="ayah 18-77" id="77" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱنطَلَقَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So they set out</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَتَّىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">until</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَتَيَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they came</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَهْلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to the) people</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَرْيَةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) a town,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱسْتَطْعَمَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they asked for food</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَهْلَهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(from) its people,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَأَبَوْاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but they refused</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُضَيِّفُوهُمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">offer them hospitality.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَوَجَدَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then they found</span></span><span class="wo