<p class="ayah 18-79" id="79" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">As for</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّفِينَةُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the ship,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَكَانَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it was</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِمَسَـٰكِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of (the) poor people</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْمَلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">working</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْبَحْرِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the sea.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَأَرَدتُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So I intended</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَعِيبَهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">I cause defect (in) it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(as there) was</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَرَآءَهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">after them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar qu