<span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَرْجُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">hoping</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِقَآءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(for the) meeting</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(with) his Lord,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلْيَعْمَلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">let him do</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَمَلاً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">deeds</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">صَـٰلِحًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">righteous</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُشْرِكْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">associate</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِعِبَادَةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in (the) worship</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّهِۦٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) his Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَحَدَۢا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">anyone."</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>110<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
